{"tid":47294,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女友一句，全車靜曬","createTime":"2016-12-20T08:57:37.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T12:13:16.000Z","uid":2936,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1efce2de7eda23e527d57e0545d5ea5841401097","tid":47294,"uid":2936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:57:37.000Z","msg":"小弟有一day由旺角返屋企，由於太夜，因此要搭亡命小巴<br />\n<br />\n在小巴上坐在司機後的一對情侶，在上車後不斷鬧交。<br />\n女的不斷鬧男是仆x，而男則鬧女的是死八婆。<br />\n經過15分鐘的「口部對戰」，男的終於忍不到，講了一句粗口。<br />\n男︰「正臭x，講極都唔明，正臭x（x為粗口也）」<br />\n女︰「如果真係臭，咁你又『奶』」<br />\n突然全車靜晒，司機減速駕駛。<br />\n<br />\n各位男士要講粗口鬧人要三思<br />\n免得把生活公諸於世。"},{"pid":"a7ba30efa1410d1354f56392f71bb4457c897157","tid":47294,"uid":27745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:58:54.000Z","msg":"AV我睇好多，我知接下來會發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"879fb3be02052a375f062cd95334de5508d7350c","tid":47294,"uid":2936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:03:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3515cd788acf8165ade0028fca2a7be5fb4d5e0f","tid":47294,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:07:25.000Z","msg":"十九幾年前既野又拎返黎講"},{"pid":"c6df95ba01d820e4d07849c7c83aaa209cdb53f5","tid":47294,"uid":22820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:08:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>AV我睇好多，我知接下來會發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n新會員hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a64be06bd08ccf87e81bbbf981d0ee321b36bd","tid":47294,"uid":44028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re